==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marketing
<hw>Mar"ket*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of selling
or of purchasing in, or as in, a market.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Articles in, or from, a market; supplies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The activities required by a producer to sell his
products, including advertising, storing, taking orders, and
distribution to vendors or individuals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Marketstead</ent>⟦br⟧
